0<br />\n1070<br />\n最高小lag<br />\n高冇問題<br />\n覺得好多野都有抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但又2頭唔到岸<br />\n有得上天下海 但直升機操控又冇bf咁靈活 但又唔似arma咁難渣<br />\n係海到上唔到船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地圖好大4個人可以鳩行 搵左任自己可以選擇做唔做<br />\n大得黎未感受到佢個價值<br />\n<br />\n好感就係有得個人化個角色<br />\n暫時就同鬼佬鳩fing多<br />\n未感受到個戰術分工運用<br />\n玩多陣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306ccdb0efe390923feb71401d3eb3fc9ceac93b","tid":106543,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T21:14:44.000Z","msg":"非常一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c5d712496ec02271098af5b5cf708608b0d57c","tid":106543,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T00:20:35.000Z","msg":"係咪純multi player open world<br />\n有冇campaign"},{"pid":"8bb7159eca34bf7f4dd86aa9887b5992049bf585","tid":106543,"uid":7508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪純multi player open world<br />\n有冇campaign</blockquote><br />\n有 campaign 嫁<br />\n咪就係open world 自己簡任務做"},{"pid":"9b78e30da5d4828356e65459208856b1c3b9cdb0","tid":106543,"uid":48015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:04:45.000Z","msg":"有無巴打有多個code<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nps4<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6773732df92896e4253ac5d6ecae5d7149f00f36","tid":106543,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"嘩玩左一晚 勁撚悶勁垃圾"},{"pid":"a0126fb69607cb2315b5649c5eac8eb22cb5adef","tid":106543,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩玩左一晚 勁撚悶勁垃圾</blockquote><br />\n一入game仲講撚到整左4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整左隻垃圾出黎<br />\n本身sell 4人小隊 大世界<br />\n但係4條友可以鳩行鳩玩 <br />\n主線講要裝滅聲 有人驚動左就變無雙<br />\n事前偵察可有可無 又冇得peek門後面<br />\n救人質 打boss 又少人又廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果學下gta v 打劫咁 有小小規劃限制會好玩好多<br />\n<br />\n個地圖堅大<br />\n出左之後應該有排玩<br />\n都係個句, 同fd玩好玩多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個系統堅廢"},{"pid":"ccd269da04b4773395626243c35e377573f06fe9","tid":106543,"uid":20937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無巴打有多個code<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nps4<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dbfac81e68aee3c706746adb5c02b34d4768f9","tid":106543,"uid":19842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:14:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無巴打有多個code<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nps4<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nps4之前登記左都無email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc4eb5e84e0e91ebff49fc264846d8a485f1554","tid":106543,"uid":4629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:06:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘩玩左一晚 勁撚悶勁垃圾</blockquote><br />\n一入game仲講撚到整左4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整左隻垃圾出黎<br />\n本身sell 4人小隊 大世界<br />\n但係4條友可以鳩行鳩玩 <br />\n主線講要裝滅聲 有人驚動左就變無雙<br />\n事前偵察可有可無 又冇得peek門後面<br />\n救人質 打boss 又少人又廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果學下gta v 打劫咁 有小小規劃限制會好玩好多<br />\n<br />\n個地圖堅大<br />\n出左之後應該有排玩<br />\n都係個句, 同fd玩好玩多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個系統堅廢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得個系統操作一開始好似啲低成本game咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過玩左個幾鐘之後還好<br />\n<br />\n可以無雙我諗因為係beta同埋呢個main mission佢都係話一星難度，所以之後個啲如果無雙應該會難過事前偵察<br />\n<br />\n佢變左open world 之後個feel其實我覺得似division, 都係周圍解任務攞嘢升級，但係就唔係looting同要玩家對戰<br />\n<br />\n我都同意如果有fd可以固定一齊煲隻game應該幾好，自己玩就有啲悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申上隻future solider幾鐘意"},{"pid":"ee5889b0aa2bda963b98b045187c1276814f8c06","tid":106543,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>嘩玩左一晚 勁撚悶勁垃圾</blockquote><br />\n一入game仲講撚到整左4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整左隻垃圾出黎<br />\n本身sell 4人小隊 大世界<br />\n但係4條友可以鳩行鳩玩 <br />\n主線講要裝滅聲 有人驚動左就變無雙<br />\n事前偵察可有可無 又冇得peek門後面<br />\n救人質 打boss 又少人又廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果學下gta v 打劫咁 有小小規劃限制會好玩好多<br />\n<br />\n個地圖堅大<br />\n出左之後應該有排玩<br />\n都係個句, 同fd玩好玩多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個系統堅廢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得個系統操作一開始好似啲低成本game咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過玩左個幾鐘之後還好<br />\n<br />\n可以無雙我諗因為係beta同埋呢個main mission佢都係話一星難度，所以之後個啲如果無雙應該會難過事前偵察<br />\n<br />\n佢變左open world 之後個feel其實我覺得似division, 都係周圍解任務攞嘢升級，但係就唔係looting同要玩家對戰<br />\n<br />\n我都同意如果有fd可以固定一齊煲隻game應該幾好，自己玩就有啲悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申上隻future solider幾鐘意</blockquote><br />\n佢優化好啲就夠<br />\n我770明明玩戰地一同FOR HONOR都重開到中高質素<br />\n黎呢到連開低都LAG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f741cefb291808ebbb7ccc7ccd9952eecbfc7fb","tid":106543,"uid":67320,"like":0,"dislike"